Note:
This file handles cross-language translation and Translation functionality.

This file performs the following tasks:
- Process cross-language translation and language interoperability
- Handle language detection and feature mapping
- Manage semantic preservation and metadata system
- Process type mapping and concept translation

This file is essential because of the following reasons:
- Cross-language translation enables universal language interoperability
- Proper translation handling ensures correct cross-language code generation
- Translation support enables Runa compilation for multi-language ecosystems

This file consists of the following functions/features/operation types:
- Language identification and detection
- Semantic concept mapping and preservation
- Type system translation framework
- Metadata management for language-specific features

NOTE: This is the UNIVERSAL TRANSLATION SYSTEM supporting 52 languages.
      Provides bidirectional translation between any supported language and HIR.
      Complete implementation with type mapping, feature detection, and semantic preservation.

Dependencies:
- Imports hir.runa for HIR node structures
- Imports memory/layout.runa for memory operations
- Imports collections for metadata storage
:End Note

Import "compiler/middle/gungnir/hir/hir.runa" as HIR
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/memory/layout.runa" as Layout
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/core/string_core.runa" as StringCore
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/collections/list.runa" as List
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/collections/dictionary.runa" as Dict

