Note: ============================================================================
Note: Language Feature Detection
Note: ============================================================================

Process called "get_language_features" takes language_id as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Get feature flags for specified language

    @Reasoning:
    Returns bitflags indicating language features for semantic mapping.
    Different languages have different type systems, memory models, etc.
    @End Reasoning

    Let features be 0

    Note: Runa language features (all features)
    If language_id is equal to LANG_RUNA:
        Set features to features plus FEAT_STATIC_TYPING
        Set features to features plus FEAT_STRONG_TYPING
        Set features to features plus FEAT_TYPE_INFERENCE
        Set features to features plus FEAT_OWNERSHIP_SYSTEM
        Set features to features plus FEAT_GARBAGE_COLLECTION
        Set features to features plus FEAT_FUNCTIONAL
        Set features to features plus FEAT_PROCEDURAL
        Return features
